title: Perfect is Impossible
itunes:title: Perfect is Impossible
description:
Episode 437 - Every human is a "perfectionism" it seems. Yet perfectionism is the enemy of creation. Perfectionism does not exist though, it is something that we make up in our heads to mask our real fears that are holding us back. Check out this episode to learn how to get past this silent killer of dreams!
